OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright and
OL,6,Fsunny evening, with largely clear
OL,7,Fskies developing overnight. Winds
OL,8,Feasing, allowing temperatures to dip
OL,9,Flow enough for a touch of frost in
OL,10,Fsome prone rural spots, particularly
OL,11,Facross eastern counties.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FAfter a chilly but sunny
OL,14,Fstart, cloud will build from the north
OL,15,Fwith patchy rain possible by midday.
OL,16,FThe rain fragmenting as it progresses,
OL,17,Fwith some parts perhaps staying dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
