OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FRemaining changeable on Tuesday with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of patchy rain clearing
OL,8,Fsouth. Turning blustery with sunny
OL,9,Fspells and heavy showers both
OL,10,FWednesday and Thursday. Feeling
OL,11,Fchilly, with a risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
